Package org.opengis.cite.kml2.c2 Description

Conformance level 2 (CL2) includes the tests for CL1 and adds tests that cover recommended constraints that should be satisfied by a KML resource. Non-conformance at this level may hinder the utility, portability, or interoperability of the resource.
See Also:
"OGC 14-068r1: OGC KML 2.3 - Abstract Test Suite", "OGC-07-134r2: OGC KML 2.2 - Abstract Test Suite"
